Vendored code from phylolm
--------------------------
This repository also includes adapted code from the CRAN package `phylolm`
(version 2.6.5), originally distributed under `GPL (>= 2) | file LICENSE`.

Vendored files:
- `R/phylolm_tools_vendor.R`
- `R/phylolm_vendor.R`

Original `phylolm` authors credited in the package metadata:
- Lam Si Tung Ho
- Cecile Ane
- Robert Lachlan
- Kelsey Tarpinian
- Rachel Feldman
- Qing Yu
- Wouter van der Bijl
- Joan Maspons
- Rutger Vos
- Paul Bastide

Local modifications were made in kfl1ou on 2026-03-08 to vendor a subset of
the likelihood code, route low-level calls through kfl1ou's bundled C
implementation, and remove unsupported paths. A copy of the upstream `phylolm`
license text is included at `inst/licenses/phylolm-LICENSE`.

